# Generated build diagnostic — a report the oils-data build writes each run (FNWL match counts,
# backfill list, property-shift deltas). It churns on every build and is not consumed by the app
# or any test, so it's a local artifact, not a tracked source of truth. (canonical-oils.json and
# canonical-oils-lite.json ARE tracked — those are the real build outputs.)
packages/oils-data/data/build-report.json
